extendedInfo.description: Cuckoos Wear Black -- Richard and Julie's Story: part 3. Graphic Novel.He thought his father was dead. Now he wishes he was. Betrayal and revenge claw at a young man's sanity as he struggles to make sense of the past.This is the third and final part of Cuckoos Wear Black -- Richard and Julie's story. By now you should have read parts 1 and 2. If you haven't, please check those out first. The app is free but if you get this far and enjoy the final part, please consider a donation to a registered charity such as Oxfam or Unicef. If you do, let me know -- always good to know :)
